{"tid":1658882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擁碩士學歷會計師行高層　涉的哥被毆案今提堂 家中檢獲衣物","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T01:10:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"640e01c763250228e4977ed18226acceb0d5c93d","tid":1658882,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"深水埗長沙灣政府合署對出上周日(6日)下午突然有的士撞向人群，兩名女子被撞倒受傷，涉事的士司機則被人拖落車圍毆，警方昨日(15日)拘捕一名32歲姓張本地男子，他今日(16日)被控及提堂。消息稱，張擁有法律碩士學歷，在本港四大會計師事務所（Big Four）中的其中一間公司任職人事部經理。<br />\n被捕男子姓張，被控一項「參與暴動」罪、一項「傷人」罪及一項「違反《禁止蒙面規例》」罪，案件將於今日下午在東區裁判法院提堂。據悉，張的寓所位於案發現場附近，警方搜查其寓所後檢獲他當日身穿的衣物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191016/mobile/bkn-20191016113949301-1016_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191016%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191016113949301-1016_00822_001.html&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=2ae144db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191016/mobile/bkn-20191016113949301-1016_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一定認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過故事教訓大家，一定要著最普通衫及要妥善處理衣服"},{"pid":"c760d514fbb4f366630943a112c173f985831d41","tid":1658882,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"91886a910d132719c310b7fa376257c68cb83fe9","tid":1658882,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可唔可以爭爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日美國眾議院通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n你當撚人condom咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse